short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add custom GPTs feature to DeepSeek

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Overview
The DeepSeek Custom GPTs Chrome extension enhances your interaction with the DeepSeek AI directly from your browser. This extension allows you to save and manage custom GPT prompts, making it easier to reuse and organize your AI interactions.

Features
Quick Interaction: Easily interact with DeepSeek from any web page.
User-Friendly Interface: Intuitive UI for seamless user experience.
Save Custom GPTs: Save custom GPT prompts with titles and content.
Display Saved Entries: View and manage saved GPT entries in a grid layout.
Delete Entries: Remove individual or all saved GPT entries.

Disclaimer
This is an independent tool and is not officially associated with DeepSeek. DeepSeek has not endorsed, sponsored, or otherwise approved this tool.
